paragraphs.title: Reading Austria OSM RDF data with SANSA N-tripleReader
paragraphs.text:
%spark
import org.apache.jena.riot.Lang
import com.typesafe.config.ConfigFactory
import net.sansa_stack.ml.spark.clustering.utils.DataProcessing
import net.sansa_stack.rdf.spark.io._


val input = "hdfs://namenode:8020/data/data/austria-pois.osm.rdf.nt"
val lang = Lang.NTRIPLES

val triples = spark.rdf(lang)(input)

triples.take(10).foreach(println)

paragraphs.title: Calculating number of neighbours around a threshold distance, Neighbors Entropy and competitiveness
paragraphs.text:
%spark

case class finddist(poi:Array[(String, Double, spatial)])

//val poiCategorySetVienna = tomTomData.poiCategoryId
       val poiCategorySetVienna = pois.map(poi => (poi.coordinate,poi.categories)).persist()
    println(pois.count())
    val locationTargetd=spatial(16.3738346,48.20817324)
    val collectted=poiCategorySetVienna.collect
    val findDistance=collectted.map(f=>distFrom(locationTargetd,f))
    val filterDistance=findDistance.filter(f=>f._2<200)
    val casefilterDistance=finddist(filterDistance)
    filterDistance.take(2).foreach(println)
    val density=filterDistance.size
    println("density="+density)
    
    //entropy
    val entropy=filterDistance.map(f=>f._1).toSet
    val countDiffernetVenues=entropy.size
    println("entropy="+countDiffernetVenues)
    
    //comeptitiveness
    val shopName="bar"
    val countCoffeShop=filterDistance.filter(f=>f._1.contains(shopName))
    val casefilterShop=finddist(countCoffeShop)
    println("percenatge of bar to total number of nearby places.  ="+(countCoffeShop.size*100/density)+"%")
